Geodetic CRS:  WGS 84
> dZ <- dZ[dZ$zoning_district == "R1-1", "zoning_district"]
> 
> stShp <- st_read("~/DropboxExternal/dataRaw/lct_000b21a_e/lct_000b21a_e.shp")
Reading layer `lct_000b21a_e' from data source 
  `/Volumes/Micron2TB/Dropbox/dataRaw/lct_000b21a_e/lct_000b21a_e.shp' 
  using driver `ESRI Shapefile'
